t by soap opera virus|date=May 19, 2006|accessdate=July 1, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/world/2006-05/19/content_595035.htm|publisher=[[China Daily]]|title=Teens suffer soap opera virus|date=May 19, 2006|accessdate=July 1, 2010}}</ref>\n\n== Cast ==\n{{main|List of Morangos com A\u00e7\u00facar cast members}}\n\n=== Notable cast deaths ===\n*'''Bernardino Esteves''' (popularly known as ''Dino'') was portrayed by [[Francisco Adam]]. The character was retired from the series after Francisco Adam died in a car accident in April 2006. In the last episode featuring Dino, the character was seen leaving in a [[hot-air balloon]], and threw his favourite orange-coloured hat onto the ground, where his lover, Susana, took it and kept it as a memento. The entire cast of the ''telenovela'' appeared and waved goodbye to the character, and the late actor who portrayed him.\n\n=== Celebrities in the series ===\n*[[Sandra Nasi\u0107]]\n*[[Sugababes]]\n*[[Reamonn]]\n*[[Simply Red]]\n*[[Daniel Bedingfield]]\n*[[Marie Serneholt]]\n*[[Greg Minnaar]]\n*[[Asher Lane]]\n*[[Melanie C]]\n*[[M\u00e3o Morta|Sapo]]\n*[[Sean Kingston]]\n*[[:pt:Carlos Andrade|Carlos Andrade]]\n*[[:pt:Pimpinha Jardim|Pimpinha Jardim]]\n*[[:pt:EZ Special|EZ Special]]\n*[[Fingertips (band)|Fingertips]]\n*[[Anjos]]\n*[[Nuno Gomes]]\n*[[Jo\u00e3o Moutinho]]\n*[[Cristovao Vilela]]\n*[[:pt:Paula Teixeira|Paula Teixeira]]\n*[[Sofia Escobar]]\n*[[David Carreira]]\n*[[Carlota Pessoa]]\n\n==Child sexual abuse==\nIn July 2012, Henrique Jales was sentenced to five years in prison for sexually abusing a child while casting for the show for TVI.<ref>http://www.ionline.pt/artigos/portugal/henrique-jales-condenado-cinco-anos-pena-suspensa</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Cl\u00e1udia Vieira]]\n*[[Benedita Pereira]]\n*[[Joana Solnado]]\n*[[H\u00e9lio Pestana]]\n*[[Mafalda Pinto]]\n*[[Teresa Tavares]]\n*[[Dalila Carmo]]\n*[[Patr\u00edcia Candoso]]\n*[[Francisco Adam]]\n*[[D\u00e2nia Neto]]\n*[[Ana Guiomar]]