12.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Luis Guzman]]]]\n[[File:Justina Machado at Queen of the South at ATX.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Justina Machado]]]]\n[[File:Rita Moreno5.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Rita Moreno]]]]\n[[File:Jon Seda at 2014 Imagen Awards.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Jon Seda]]]]\n[[File:Jimmy Smits by Gage Skidmore.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Jimmy Smits]]]]\n[[File:Benicio Del Toro - Guardians of the Galaxy premiere - July 2014 (cropped).jpg|thumb|140px|[[Benicio del Toro]]]]\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Ferrer]]{{Snd}} actor\n* [[Miguel Ferrer]]{{Snd}} actor, ''[[Crossing Jordan]]''; son of Jos\u00e9 Ferrer\n* [[Rafael Ferrer (actor)|Rafael Ferrer]]{{Snd}} actor; son of Jos\u00e9 Ferrer\n* [[Franky G]]{{Snd}} film and television actor\n* [[Gloria Garayua]]{{Snd}} film and television actress\n* [[Aimee Garcia]]{{Snd}} father is from [[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]]<ref>http://gozamos.com/2011/11/interview-aimee-garcia/?doing_wp_cron=1385765785.4875979423522949218750</ref> \n* [[Mayte Garc\u00eda]]{{Snd}} American dancer, actress, singer, and choreographer\n* [[Marilyn Ghigliotti]]{{Snd}} character actress, ''[[Clerks]]''\n* [[Ian Gomez]]{{Snd}} actor, known for his comedic TV work, ''[[Felicity (TV series)|Felicity]]'', ''[[Cougar Town]]''\n* [[Marga Gomez]]{{Snd}} comedian, playwright, and humorist\n* [[Reagan Gomez-Preston]]{{Snd}} American actress of Puerto Rican and African descent<ref>http://elblogdehola.blogspot.com/2011/05/betcha-didnt-know.html El Blog de HOLA</ref>\n* [[Rick Gonzalez]]{{Snd}} actor, film ''Coach Carter'', television series ''Reaper''\n* [[La'Myia Good]]{{Snd}} actress\n* [[Meagan Good]]{{Snd}} actress\n* [[Camille Guaty]]{{Snd}} actress\n* [[Luis Guzm\u00e1n]]{{Snd}} actor\n* [[April Lee Hern\u00e1ndez]]{{Snd}} actress\n* [[Kristin Herrera]]{{Snd}} actress, ''[[Zoey 101]]''\n* [[Jon Huertas]]{{Snd}} American actor, ''[[Castle (TV series)|Castle]]''; of Puerto Rican and African descent<ref>[http://eldia.com.do/jon-huertas-siempre-supe-que-algun-dia-iba-a-vivir-y-trabajar-en-hollywood/ El 