roche_r.html |archivedate=2007-08-14 }} Troche, Rose</ref>\n* [[Alanna Ubach]]{{Snd}} American actress; of Puerto Rican and Mexican descent<ref>[http://www.latina.com/entertainment/celebrity/15-more-stars-you-never-knew-were-latino?slide=9 \"15 (More) Stars You Never Knew Were Latino!\"] 06/11/2010, Latina</ref>\n* [[Nadine Velazquez]]{{Snd}} American actress; of Puerto Rican descent<ref>Maxim Magazine October 8th 2008, Interview Page 78</ref>\n* [[Desiree Marie Velez]]{{Snd}} American actress\n* [[Lauren V\u00e9lez]]{{Snd}} American actress, ''[[Dexter (TV series)|Dexter]]''; of Puerto Rican descent\n* [[Loraine V\u00e9lez]]{{Snd}} American actress; Puerto Rican parents; sister of Lauren V\u00e9lez\n* [[Christina Vidal]]{{Snd}} American actress; of Puerto Rican parents<ref>[http://www.timeforkids.com/TFK/teachers/wr/article/0,27972,101294,00.html Time For Kids | Classroom | Home | TFK Q&A: Christina Vidal<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724021440/http://www.timeforkids.com/TFK/teachers/wr/article/0%2C27972%2C101294%2C00.html |date=2011-07-24 }}</ref>\n* [[Lisa Vidal]]{{Snd}} American actress; of Puerto Rican descent<ref>http://www.tv3.co.nz/Lisa-Vidal-as-Christina-Martinez/tabid/1393/articleID/66201/Default.aspx Lisa Vidal (as Christina Martinez){{Snd}} Character Bios</ref>\n* [[Holly Woodlawn]]{{Snd}} Puerto Rican-born transgender actress and former Warhol superstar\n* [[David Zayas]]{{Snd}} American theatrical, film, and television actor, ''[[Dexter (TV series)|Dexter]]''; Puerto Rican born and American raised<ref>[http://www.hollywoodpoker.com/green-room/celebrity-poker/biographies/david-zayas.html HollywoodPoker.com:David Zayas]</ref>\n\n== Directors, producer and screenwriters of films, theater and TV ==\n* [[Miguel Arteta]]{{Snd}} Puerto Rican film and television director; film ''[[The Good Girl]]''; television series ''[[Six Feet Under (TV series)|Six Feet Under]]''\n* [[Ivonne Bel\u00e9n]]{{Snd}} Puerto Rican d