ichelle Font]]{{Snd}} beauty queen; Miss Washington USA; competed in the 2008 Miss USA pageant; of Cuban and Puerto Rican descent\n* [[Jaslene Gonzalez]]{{Snd}} Puerto Rican-American model, Puerto Rican born<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.misquincemag.com/quinceanera-picture-stories/celebrity/jaslene-gonzalez|title = Jaslene Gonzalez|publisher = Mis Quince Magazine| date = February 5, 2008}}</ref> and American raised<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.extranews.net/news.php?nid=2783&clave=a%3A1%3A%7Bi%3A0%3Bs%3A7%3A%22jaslene%22%3B%7D|publisher = Gonzalez Extra Newspaper|title = title|url-status = dead|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928075350/http://www.extranews.net/news.php?nid=2783&clave=a%3A1%3A%7Bi%3A0%3Bs%3A7%3A%22jaslene%22%3B%7D|archivedate = 2007-09-28}}</ref>\n* [[Melanie Iglesias]]{{Snd}} American model and actress; of Puerto Rican, Italian, and Filipino heritage<ref>[http://www.worldsmostbeautiful.com/2011/08/05/melanie-iglesias-wild-card/ Wild Card].</ref>\n* [[Danielle Polanco]]{{Snd}} dancer and choreographer; Dominican-Puerto Rican American\n* [[Pam Rodriguez]]{{Snd}} American [[glamour model]]; of Guatemalan and Puerto Rican descent<ref>{{cite news|title=Pam Rodriguez interview |date=2008-06-11 |url=http://www.oyemag.com/index.php/pam-rodriguez/ |work=Open Your Eyes Magazine |accessdate=2009-12-24 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091224132450/http://www.oyemag.com/index.php/pam-rodriguez/ |archivedate=2009-12-24 }}</ref>\n* [[Jock Soto]]{{Snd}} principal ballet dancer with the [[New York City Ballet]]\n\n== Sports ==\n[[File:Carmelo Anthony Nov 2013.jpg|thumb|140px|[[Carmelo Anthony]]]]\n* [[Benjamin Agosto]]{{Snd}} American figure skater; Puerto Rican father, American mother of Romanian and Russian descent<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenskate.com/articles/2002/042803.shtml |title=Interview with Ice Dancers Benjamin Agosto and Tanith Belbin |publisher=goldenskate.com |date=April 28, 2003 |accessdate=April 